&lt;p id="yT7eGB"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Warcraft I &lt;/em&gt;and &lt;em&gt;Warcraft II &lt;/em&gt;are being delisted from GOG “at the publisher’s request,” the company says. Their publisher,...&lt;/p&gt;
